{"tid":1548831,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講好左核彈都唔割呢？","createTime":"2019-09-07T06:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T06:52:29.000Z","uid":148185,"like":7,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"a3b4352db4a8527a0ad93b28a4d7a698acb40a18","tid":1548831,"uid":148185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:28:27.000Z","msg":"你班仆街見到燒山就屌晒鬼？<br />\n有冇諗過依位手足真係抱住攬炒既心態去抗爭<br />\n咁多野發生咗，死既死傷既傷<br />\n口講核彈都唔割係因為未燒到你地度<br />\n你地就係怕有一日要到自己承擔先咁快割蓆<br />\n你地要做乜都冇人阻止過<br />\n點解一聽到攬炒就淆晒青要阻人？<br />\n對唔對得住付左血汗同生命既咁多位？<br />\n佢係要做我地就全力支持<br />\n<br />\n我希望核彈都唔割唔係得把口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439485fb6a8c3c2bc7adb8dc330a03abf3e94008","tid":1548831,"uid":107663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:28:49.000Z","msg":"知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"706625ced96bff79db0c816a8c2d5f6f9d774bab","tid":1548831,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:28:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c796bd9ebc9f6229f14440461d10891498c7a92c","tid":1548831,"uid":25108,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:29:33.000Z","msg":"何解燒山=攬炒?<br />\n咁你燒自己咪得囉"},{"pid":"4de04035f69f15004cbef01d3a4ddc38fc6af1f9","tid":1548831,"uid":22360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:30:42.000Z","msg":"個核彈最好唔好掟落自己友到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4555c37102ae661abbe2e3ac66282c04a9750a","tid":1548831,"uid":284264,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T06:30:44.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無人話割<br />\n只係唔合理就要指出<br />\n<br />\n不如你講下燒山點解對運動有益？<br />\n我只睇到地產商會好開心wor<br />\n<br />\n請大家善用不推文回覆</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"18